# Frontend Patterns

## RTK Query API
Location: `client/src/helper/APIs/`
```typescript
export const exampleApi = createApi({
  reducerPath: 'exampleApi',
  baseQuery: fetchBaseQuery({ baseUrl: '/api', credentials: 'include' }),
  endpoints: (builder) => ({
    getData: builder.query({ query: () => ({ url: 'endpoint' }) }),
    updateData: builder.mutation({ query: (data) => ({ url: 'endpoint', method: 'POST', body: { data } }) }),
  }),
});
```

## Common Hooks
- `useDebounce(value, delay)` - Debounce values
- `useLocalStorage(key, initial)` - Persistent state
- `usePolling(callback, interval)` - Polls when app active
- `useIsFeatureFlagEnabled(name)` - Feature flag check
- `useTheme()` - Dark/light/system theme

## Toast/Notifications
```typescript
const { addSnackbar } = useSnackbar();
addSnackbar({ title: 'Error', message: error.message, pVariant: 'destructive' });
// Variants: 'default' | 'destructive' | 'success' | 'warning'
```

